AppBackgroundServices - Class in com.kaiserware.sailingrace
IntentService Class to handle these tasks independent of the UI: 1) receive the apparent wind data from the SailTimerAPI app (if Windex is enabled) 2) convert Apparent wind data to True wind data 3) write wind data to the sqlite DB 4) update COG/SOG/Wind values in global parameters This IntentService will continue to run in the background even if user hits either the Home key to work on some other App else on the devise or hits the power button.
